title: HQD CUVIE PLUS 1200 PUFFS 6CT
description: HQD Cuvie Plus is a revolutionary 1200 puff disposable pod device designed to be a rewarding alternative to cigarettes. This compact AIO disposable device includes an 850mAh battery module and a pre-filled e-liquid pod containing 50mg of salt nicotine. The resolute aluminum exterior allows for a reliable device that is ergonomic due to its discreet, cylindrical design. The 850mAh inbuilt battery means that this is a long-lasting device, the level of charge is indicated through the LED light at the base of the device. With an inhale activation, there is no maintenance required just simply inhale straight away to begin vaping. What makes HQD Cuvie Plus so impressive is the number of puffs and e-juice capacity. The capacity of 5ml e-juice is an amazing number. Few small disposable pods have such a large pod capacity. HQD Cuvie Plus can last up to 1200 puffs. The concentration of nicotine is about 50mg, which is enough to eliminate your craving for nicotine. Provide a variety of flavor options, is perfect for vaping on the go.HQD CUVIE PLUS 1200 PUFFS FEATURES :Portable, Ergonomic Design850mAh built-in battery for 1200 puffsPre-charged and Ready to VapeDraw to Activate Firing MechanismPre-filled 5.0mL E-juice5% Nicotine Salt StrengthPC+Aluminum materials, durable & lightMultiple Premium Flavor
Variation: APPLE PEACH,BLUEBERRY,ENERGY DRINK,GRAPEY,ICED MINT,LUSH ICE,LYCHEE ICE,MANGO ICE,PINA COLADA,PINEAPPLE
